{"tid":1568603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"晦氣撚全面退場★行動撚全面進場","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:55:07.000Z","uid":38071,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcd2b9e437f6aa6f2589e1fff47666e2dccb186","tid":1568603,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"你班傻仔幾時先醒<br />\n做怨婦係唔會說服到人聽你講<br />\n講晦氣說話只會將人越屌越遠<br />\n<br />\n自己認同嘅嘢就自己直接行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道每個人嘅判斷都唔同，你直接做出嚟就最show到俾人睇你嘅idea有幾好。<br />\n<br />\n人地判斷唔同你點屌點鬧都唔會改變到佢判斷，除非你直接俾個效果佢地睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各自爬山，拒絕分化"},{"pid":"6d9c90783f0b338abce878657a9aa4dbc509fba7","tid":1568603,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a770631fc61fc21e699f2d309d4012c9eec43a92","tid":1568603,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你個臭街！<br />\n今日死差佬同藍絲又周圍打人！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n聽日九月十五日<br />\n<br />\n2pm<br />\n 銅鑼灣東角道 /<br />\n維園 / 英領<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 全人類同我出黎！<br />\n唔係我屌埋你老母呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/915/652/b49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F915%2F652%2Fb49.gif&h=c007be28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"ea6f58f3ca9371460a929a55a599481a55ed029c","tid":1568603,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7917dc3e862d3fa1c2fe2407b94cf1621770d62e","tid":1568603,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"我相信唔認同去送頭嘅手足唔會對肯出嚟抵抗暴徒嘅手足落井下石<br />\n我同樣相信出咗嚟嘅手足會明